                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980110-73-off400 t17980110-73-cd401"></join>, a silver table-spoon, value 8s. and three silver teaspoons, value 4s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17980110-73-victim730" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Nott
